Quiz 45 Baked GI

1. Rank the following in terms of their photo realism (highest to lowest)

D. Directional Specular
A. Directional
B. Non-directional
C. Direct Lighting Only

2. When would you make the game design choice to use fog?

- To not render objects that are far away in the scene

3. What is the default source of Ambient Light?

- The Skybox

4. What type of object does this property take?

- A Direction Light

5. What is the default source of reflections (without any reflection probes in the scene)?

- The Skybox